WEBVTT

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:31.216
They're more likely to do drugs,
more likely to go to jail,

00:09:31.240 --> 00:09:33.536
more likely to drop out of high school,

00:09:33.560 --> 00:09:34.976
and most importantly,

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:37.216
they're more likely
to do to their children

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:39.080
what their parents did to them.

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:42.736
This trauma, this chaos in the home,

00:09:42.760 --> 00:09:46.216
is our culture's
very worst gift to our children,

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:48.760
and it's a gift that keeps on giving.

00:09:50.280 --> 00:09:52.096
So you combine all that,

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:54.816
the hopelessness, the despair,

00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:57.176
the cynicism about the future,

00:09:57.200 --> 00:09:58.440
the childhood trauma,

00:09:59.440 --> 00:10:01.336
the low social capital,